---
title: "constructor (PriceManager)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_validate: verifierProxy == address(0)?
    q_validate --> q_error: true
    q_error --> [*]: revert Errors.InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_validate --> q_set_proxy: false
    q_set_proxy --> q_check_feeds: i_streamsVerifierProxy = IVerifierProxy(verifierProxy)
    q_check_feeds --> q_apply: feedsInfo.length > 0
    q_check_feeds --> q_emit: feedsInfo.length == 0
    q_apply --> q_emit: _applyFeedInfoUpdates(feedsInfo, [])
    q_emit --> [*]: emit VerifierProxySet(verifierProxy)

    note right of q_validate
        INV-001: verifierProxy must not be zero address
        INV-002: i_streamsVerifierProxy is immutable after construction
    end note
